{"type": "article", "id": 24932, "title": "有自然特征的极简家具组", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-05T07:03:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 34, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702120312ptZTfeVGEJ2oIxqU.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这组家具来自丹麦 VIA 大学的学生，一共 12 种，在今年的斯德哥尔摩家具展上展出。他们都运用木头等材料打造生活中常见的家具，有自己个性和特征。比如挂在墙上的半圆形置物盒，可以像抽屉一样拉开，造型简洁而带着自然的特征。一款沙发有两个像花瓣一样的环绕式靠背，一大一小相互交错，赋予了沙发柔和自然的色彩。<a href=\"http://en.via.dk/programmes/design/gallery/stockholm-furniture-fair-2016\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120309lIAQYJTcG6yLBrtK.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120310tC1BHrQbEikW3gyT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120310q1rCJnhV7QIFtHZ8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.99666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120311mzRY43M6kq0fgdCw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.79\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120311qpIsk0NX1UGRn7l8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021203120Rp1rAghik2cwfPu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}